dc_title_s: Turtle Nesting Sites on the Eastern Coast of Kenya, 2006
dc_description_s: This point shapefile contains locations of turtle nesting and breeding sites on the eastern coast of Kenya.This data was used in Map 6.4 and Map 6.5 in Nature's Benefits in Kenya: An Atlas of Ecosystems and Human Well-Being.
dc_creator_sm: Kenya Marine and Fisheries Research Institute
